snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 3 | Official Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
It’s time to play the final games.
Squid Game Season 3. June 27.
Only on Netflix.

More info on Squid Game Season 3:
A failed rebellion, the death of a friend, and a secret betrayal. Picking up in the aftermath of Season 2’s bloody cliffhanger, the third and final season of Netflix’s most popular series finds Gi-hun, a.k.a. Player 456, at his lowest point yet. But the Squid Game stops for no one, so Gi-hun will be forced to make some important choices in the face of overwhelming despair as he and the surviving players are thrust into deadlier games that test everyone’s resolve. With each round, their choices lead to increasingly grave consequences. Meanwhile, In-ho resumes his role as Front Man to welcome the mysterious VIPs, and his brother Jun-ho continues his search for the elusive island, unaware there’s a traitor in their midst. Will Gi-hun make the right decisions, or will Front Man finally break his spirit?
Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys®, becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Season 3 stars Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Wi Ha-jun, Park Gyu-young, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Jo Yu-ri, Chae Kuk-hee, Lee David, Roh Jae-won, and Jun Suk-ho, with special appearance by Park Hee-soon.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81615967

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

snippet.title: PM Narendra Modi is “Besharam”, “Darpok” and “Must Apologise” to India for Pahalgam: Satya Pal Malik
snippet.description:
Modi is "besharam", "darpok" and "must apologize" to the country for Pahalgam: Satya Pal Malik, the last Governor of Jammu and Kashmir, to Karan Thapar for The Wire.

..........................................


In what will seem like an no-holds-barred sharply critical interview, Satya Pal Malik, the last Governor of Jammu and Kashmir, has said that Prime Minister Modi is “besharam” (shameless), “darpok” (cowardly) and “must apologize” to the country for permitting Pahalgam to happen. Mr. Malik was also outspokenly critical of Mr. Modi’s failure to attend the all-party meeting or to praise the Kashmiri people for their emotional and powerful response to the Pahalgam terrorist attack in his Mann Ki Baat. Mr. Malik said the failure to attend the all-party meeting was a sign of “arrogance” whilst he suggested that Mr. Modi did not praise the Kashmiri response because he benefits politically from permitting a Hindu-Muslim divide to continue in the country.

 

In a 25-minute interview to Karan Thapar for The Wire, Mr. Malik, who has also served as Governor in Bihar, Meghalaya, Goa and Odisha, and was Governor in Jammu and Kashmir during the Pulwama terrorist attack of 2019, said that serious intelligence failure and security lapses lay behind the Pahalgam attack. I will leave you to get the details from the interview.

 

However, speaking specifically about the Kashmir security review meetings recently held by Mr. Amit Shah, one of which was just days before the Pahalgam attack, Mr. Malik said that these were not security reviews but more like social gatherings where people meet for lunch and what he called “gup-shup”.

 

Speaking about the present Lieutenant Governor of Jammu and Kashmir, Manoj Sinha, who, in the first instance, is responsible for security, Mr. Malik said he should have accepted moral responsibility and immediately resigned.

 

In the interview, Mr. Malik spoke about the demolition of houses of people who are suspected to be terrorists without any due process whatsoever. He spoke about arrests of up to 2,000 people, again, entirely on suspicion which he believes happened primarily because they are Kashmiri and Muslim and for no other reason. He spoke about the treatment of Kashmiris outside Kashmir. He spoke about hateful comments made by the President of the Hindu Sena. He spoke about the media’s failure to effectively report the actual response of the Kashmiri people. He believes the media has let down the country.

 

I will stop there. You should see the interview for yourself. Mr. Malik speaks almost entirely in Hindi. The questions are mainly in English but there are some in Hindi.

In what will seem like an no-holds-barred sharply critical interview, Satya Pal Malik, the last Governor of Jammu and Kashmir, has said that Prime Minister Modi is “besharam” (shameless), “darpok” (cowardly) and “must apologize” to the country for permitting Pahalgam to happen. Mr. Malik was also outspokenly critical of Mr. Modi’s failure to attend the all-party meeting or to praise the Kashmiri people for their emotional and powerful response to the Pahalgam terrorist attack in his Mann Ki Baat. Mr. Malik said the failure to attend the all-party meeting was a sign of “arrogance” whilst he suggested that Mr. Modi did not praise the Kashmiri response because he benefits politically from permitting a Hindu-Muslim divide to continue in the country.

 

In a 25-minute interview to Karan Thapar for The Wire, Mr. Malik, who has also served as Governor in Bihar, Meghalaya, Goa and Odisha, and was Governor in Jammu and Kashmir during the Pulwama terrorist attack of 2019, said that serious intelligence failure and security lapses lay behind the Pahalgam attack. I will leave you to get the details from the interview.

 

However, speaking specifically about the Kashmir security review meetings recently held by Mr. Amit Shah, one of which was just days before the Pahalgam attack, Mr. Malik said that these were not security reviews but more like social gatherings where people meet for lunch and what he called “gup-shup”.

 

Speaking about the present Lieutenant Governor of Jammu and Kashmir, Manoj Sinha, who, in the first instance, is responsible for security, Mr. Malik said he should have accepted moral responsibility and immediately resigned.

 

In the interview, Mr. Malik spoke about the demolition of houses of people who are suspected to be terrorists without any due process whatsoever. He spoke about arrests of up to 2,000 people, again, entirely on suspicion which he believes happened primarily because they are Kashmiri and Muslim and for no other reason. He spoke about the treatment of Kashmiris outside Kashmir. He spoke about hateful comments made by the President of the Hindu Sena. He spoke about the media’s failure to effectively report the actual response of the Kashmiri people. He believes the media has let down the country.

 

I will stop there. You should see the interview for yourself. Mr. Malik speaks almost entirely in Hindi. The questions are mainly in English but there are some in Hindi.

snippet.title: Rishta Pakka Samjhe?  | Take A Break
snippet.description:
In Rishta Pakka Samjhe?, witness the ultimate face-off: two families, one living room, and the high-stakes game of Indian arranged marriage! 😬🍵

When a boy's family visits a girl's house "just to see the girl," the awkward tension, silent judgments, forced smiles, and over-serving of snacks begin! From overenthusiastic aunties asking weird questions to the parents pretending they’re not desperate, this sketch hilariously captures every stereotype of the great Indian rishta process.

Will this meet-and-greet end with a wedding date or a polite “hum soch ke batate hain”? Watch now to find out!

#RishtaPakkaSamjhe #ArrangedMarriageComedy #IndianShaadi #DesiFamilies #FunnySketch #ShaadiRishta #YouTubeComedy

Produced By - Monica Prabhudesai

snippet.title: Panchayat Season 4 - Official Teaser | Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav | Prime Video IN
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Panchayat Season 4 Official Teaser
Starring Jitendra Kumar, Neena Gupta, Raghubir Yadav, Faisal Malik, Chandan Roy, Sanvikaa
Created by Deepak Kumar Mishra, Chandan Kumar
Directed by Akshat Vijaywargiya, Deepak Kumar Mishra
Written by Chandan Kumar
Executive Producers: Deepak Kumar Mishra, Vijay Koshy, Shreyansh Pandey
A TVF Creation

Official Release Date July 2, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Amid intense village panchayat elections, Pradhan and Bhushan’s camps battle through sharp political moves. As Abhishek sheds his neutrality, both his future and Pradhan’s hang in the balance.

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.description:

Step into Jethalal’s world with Gada Electronics!  Manage the shop, tackle quirky customers, and experience nonstop TMKOC-style fun. Are you ready for the challenge? 

 Play now: https://gadaelectronics.page.link/dhgB  #GadaElectronics #TMKOCGame


Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: किसके धमकी भरे Call से उड़ गए Jethalal के होश? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Funny Hits
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to Sony PAL: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCw7xjxzbMwgBSmbeYwqYRMg

Tapu Sena informs all the members of Gokuldham Society about Project Roshni and also collects donations from all the members. All the members of Gokuldham society appreciate Tapu Sena's efforts as they all are working for a noble cause. Later, Tapu Sena gets upset, as instead of collecting Rs. 25,000 they have managed to collect only Rs.1850. Tapu finds his loopholes and decides to find an alternate way to achieve the target.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episode No - 1005 & 1006
Produced By -  Asit Kumarr Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sonypal #Latest #tmkoc #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly revolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises.

Click Here To Watch More Episodes Of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLfyXOEyr93G39ERvvEQcKo4oN7c826eVu

snippet.description:

Episode 4390: Gogi Ka Online Course
--------------------------------------------------------
Gogi finds a chance to speak to Sonu and asks her for financial help. Later, he also turns to Pinku for money. Will Gogi succeed in recovering his lost funds?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4390 | 6 May 2025
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2025 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/shows/taarak-mehta-ka-ooltah-chashmah-1090477312

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #SAB

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah: 
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7ZFhouqhrvP3Sx0U7qxdzJi

snippet.title: Ek Main Aur Ek Tu Hai | Hai Junoon! | Sunidhi Chauhan, Jacqueline Fernandez, Priyank, Santana,Akshay
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai: 😯 Ruhi को लगेगा झटका, Daksh का राज बदलेगा सबकी जिंदगी #hotnews
snippet.description:
#YeRishtaKyaKehelataHai #YRKKH #SaasBahuAurSaazish #SBS #abhira #armaan 

*Yeh Rishta Kya Kehlata Hai* is a long-running Indian television drama that explores family relationships, love, and societal dynamics through its evolving storylines. The show, which began with Akshara and Naitik's journey, has progressed through generations, maintaining its core theme of familial bonds. In the current track, the focus has shifted to a new generation, highlighting the lives of Abhira (the union of Abhimanyu and Akshara's legacy), Armaan, and Ruhi. These characters navigate their relationships, ambitions, and the challenges of their lineage while upholding the values of the Goenka and Birla families. The blend of drama, emotions, and cultural nuances continues to resonate with viewers, ensuring its enduring popularity.

Watch Saas Bahu aur Saazish (SBS) on ABP News daily at 2:30 PM to know what's happening in Indian television and bollywood industry with Aditi Arora Sawant. Presenting you the latest updates and daily dose of entertainment in the form of star cast interviews, gossips, updates of reality shows, behind the scenes, twist in serials. Join the non stop entertainment with Saas Bahu aur Saazish for all the cool and juicy news.

टेलीविजन और बॉलीवुड इंडस्ट्री के बारे में जानने के लिए एबीपी न्यूज़ पर देखिये सास बहु और साज़िश (एसबीएस) अदिति रॉव सावंत के साथ  रोज़ाना 2:30 बजे। एसबीएस पेश करता है स्टार कास्ट के इंटरव्यू, रियलिटी शो के अपडेट, सीरियल्स के नए मोड़, परदे के पीछे की कुछ गपशप और भी बहुत कुछ। नॉन स्टॉप मनोरंजन के लिए शामिल हों सास बहू और साज़िश के साथ।

snippet.title: Prakash Varma Exclusive Interview | Thudarum | Mohanlal | Conversation with Maneesh Narayanan
snippet.description:
'ലാലേട്ടന്റെ ഇടി സ്‌ക്രീനിൽ പവർഫുൾ, ലൊക്കേഷനിൽ ദേഹത്ത് തൊട്ടിട്ടില്ല. തരുൺ ഗംഭീര ഫിലിം മേക്കർ ആണ്. ജോർജ് സാറിന്റെ 'ഹലോ' വന്നത് എങ്ങനെ? ലാലേട്ടന്റെ കൂടെ അഭിനയിക്കുന്നത് ഭീകര വെല്ലുവിളി'

ഇന്ത്യയിലെ ഏറ്റവും പ്രധാനപ്പെട്ട പരസ്യചിത്ര സംവിധായകനും, നിർവാണയുടെ സ്ഥാപകനുമായ പ്രകാശ് വർമ ‘തുടരും’ സിനിമയെ കുറിച്ചും, ജോർജ്ജ് സാർ എന്ന കഥാപാത്രത്തെ കുറിച്ചും, പരസ്യചിത്ര സംവിധായകനായുള്ള 25 വർഷത്തെ കരിയറിനെ കുറിച്ചും ക്യു സ്റ്റുഡിയോ എഡിറ്റർ മനീഷ് നാരായണനുമായി നടത്തിയ അഭിമുഖം ഒന്നാം ഭാഗം. 

Location: Nakshathra Mana

0:00 - 1:20 Prevue

1:21 - 5:53 Tharun is extraordinary film maker

5:55 - 9:03 Thudarum casting

9:36 - 14:49 The decision to act in 'Thudarum' was challenging

14:50 - 18:30 The audition that impressed Mohanlal

18:32 - 23:55 Nirvana

23:57 - 25:00 advertising career

25:01 - 27:41 CI George Mathan

27:42 - 31:07 Lalettan protected me like a big brother

31:08 - 32.:6  climax scene with shobhana

32:47 - 37:47 First scene with mohanlal

37:51 - 42:53  ആക്ഷൻ പറഞ്ഞാൽ മോഹൻലാൽ പിന്നെ ബെൻസ് ആണ്

42:54 - 46:31  I miss being on set

46:32 - 48:18 Rejaputhra Renjith is another person who influenced me

48:19 - 50:29 Reason behind the success of 'Thudarum

50:30 - 52:01 I'm enjoying being on the set

snippet.title: Rakesh Barot | Te Rakhiya Na Ghar Na Ghat Na | તે રાખ્યા ના ઘર ના ઘાટ ના | Gujarati Bewafa Song 2025
snippet.description:
Check out the new Gujarati bewafa song by Rakesh Barot, "Te Rakhiya Na Ghar Na Ghat Na" only on  @SaregamaGujarati   💔🎶

રાકેશ બારોટનું નવું ગુજરાતી બેવફા ગીત "તે રખિયા ના ઘર ના ઘાટ ના" સાંભળો, માત્ર @SaregamaGujarati  પર

Credits:
Singer: Rakesh Barot
Producer: Red Velvet Cinema 
Artist: Rakesh Barot. Neha Suthar, Dharmesh Joshi 
Concept: Purvi Vasava, Pranav Jethava
Music: Mayur Nadiya 
Lyrics: Vipul Raval
Director: Pranav Jethava jp 
DOP: Chirag Kachhia  
Creative Head: Dhyey Films & Team
Technical Support: Jenish Talaviya
Choreographer: Dipak Turi
Mack-up hair: Hasmukh Limbachiya 
Rakesh Barot Costume: Manisha R Barot
Light: Kalpesh Jadav 
Production: Satubha, Jigar panchal 
Spot: Raju Akshay 
Poster: Raj Charoliya

Lyrics:
હે તને લાગશે નેહકા ગોડી મારા રે પ્રેમ ના 
હે તને લાગશે નેહકા અરે મારા રે પ્રેમ ના (2)
તે રાખીયા તે અમને ઘર ના કે ઘાટ ના 
હે જીવ મારો તારી યાદ મા ગાજે ચમ ગગનમાં 
તારા વગર મારા દાડા જશે ચમ ના 
અમે રહી ગયા ગોડી તારા માટે સાવ ખાલી નોમ  ના 
હે તને લાગશે નેહકા મારા રે પ્રેમ ના 
ઓ રોજ તારા ગોમ ના સેમળે આપડે મળતા 
તારા માટે નવી નવી વસ્તુ અમે લાવતા 
તમારા પ્રેમ ની અમે કદર ઘણી કરતા 
આજે મારા પ્રેમ ની ગણ નથી કરતા 
હે મારા પ્રેમ નું પ્રમાણ ના રાખીયું 
ચમ પગે કમાડ વાગિયું તારા વિરહ મા અમે રાત દાડો રોવાના 
અમે રહી ગયા ગોડી તારા માટે સાવ ખાલી નોમ  ના 
હે તને લાગશે નેહકા ગોડી મારા રે પ્રેમ ના
તે રાખીયા તે અમને ઘર ના કે ઘાટ ના 
હો તારું ઘણું રખિયું તોય ચઢી ગઈ તું માથે 
અમારે જીવવું હતું વ્હાલી તારી સાથે 
ફેરવા પથ્થર ફરે એમ તુ તો પણ ફરી ગઈ 
રાજ કરાયું રાણી જેમ તોય મારી ના થઈ 
હે મારા પ્રેમ નું વળી દીધું રોટન 
થોય ગયું મારે સિગરેટ નું વ્યશન 
મારા પ્રેમ મા ભલીવાર ના આયો ના 
અમે રહી ગયા ગોડી તારા માટે સાવ ખાલી નોમ  ના
 હે તને લાગશે નેહકા ગોડી મારા રે પ્રેમ ના 
તે રાખીયા તે અમને ઘર ના કે ઘાટ ના

snippet.title: BREAKING: Pakistan state TV says two Indian jets have been shot down | India-Pakistan conflict
snippet.description:
State-run Pakistan Television has reported that the country's air force shot down two Indian jets.

It is not clear if the aircraft were in Pakistan airspace or if they were involved in India's attack on targets in the country. 

India says it hit what it claimed were terrorist facilities following an attack in Kashmir last week.

snippet.title: Ting Ling Sajna | Bhool Chuk Maaf | Rajkummar Rao, Dhanashree | Tanishk, Irshad, Madhubanti Bagchi
snippet.description:
Aag bhi hun main, Shola bhi hun 🔥
Main hi thanda paani! 🌊

Presenting the fourth single ‘Ting Ling Sajna’ from ‘Bhool Chuk Maaf’, featuring Rajkummar Rao and Dhanashree! Composed by Tanishk Bagchi, penned by Irshad Kamil and sung by Madhubanti Bagchi and Tanishk Bagchi; this song is sure to set you on fire! 

#TingLingSajna #RajkummarRao #Dhanashree #WamiqaGabbi #TanishkBagchi #IrshadKamil #MadhubantiBagchi

Title: Ting Ling Sajna  
Singer: Madhubanti Bagchi & Tanishk Bagchi  
Composer: Tanishk Bagchi 
Music Production: Tanishk Bagchi & Ganesh Waghela 
Additional Production: Param Raj 
Lyricist: Irshad Kamil 
Language: Hindi
Mix Master: Eric Pillai @ Future sound of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai 
Director of Photography: Manu Anand 
Director of Choreography: Vijay A Ganguly

Maddock Films presents #BhoolChukMaaf
In cinemas on 9th May
Cast - Rajkummar Rao, Wamiqa Gabbi, Sanjay Mishra, Seema Pahwa, Zakir Hussain, Raghubir Yadav, Ishtiyak Khan, Anubha Fatehpuria
Produced By: Dinesh Vijan 
Directed By: Karan Sharma 
Co-Producers: Sharada Karki Jalota 
Music By: Tanishk Bagchi 
Background Score: Ketan Sodha 
Story Screenplay & Dialogues By: Karan Sharma 
Director Of Photography: Sudeep Chatterjee 
Lyricist: Irshad Kamil
Costume Designer: Sheetal Iqbal Sharma
Associate Producer: Vineeta S Tanwar

Lyrics:
Main ban than ke rijhaati hun
Hatati hun main har parda
Tu mujhko Dard de dena
Koi meetha sa bedarda

Pyara mujhe tu laga hai
Soya irada jaga hai
Mana kare to daga hai

Aankhon ne teri thaga hai
Sooni si ye to jagah hai
Seene mein hone hai

Ke jese Tingling sajna sajna…2 

Aisa koi jalwa dikha de goriye 
Jo ki saari duniya bhula de goriye 
Sholon jaisi tapti jawani hai teri 
Thoda mujhe Ismein jala de goriye

Aag bhi hun main shola bhi hun 
Main hi thanda paani

Aaj tumhari hun main lekin
Kal ko main begaani 

Meri chaukhat pe aate hain
Ashiq pyaase pyaase

Pyar badhana pyaas bujhana
Mera dhandha paani

Tingling sajna sajna…2 

Main ban than ke rijhaati hun
Hatati hun main har parda
Tu mujhko Dard de dena
Koi meetha sa bedarda

Jaise kahegi karunga
Paani main tera bharunga 
Mauka na jaane main dunga 

Seene mein tere rahunga 
Leharon mein teri bahunga 
Kanon mein tere kahunga 

Tingling Sajna, Tu hai meri 
Tingling Sajna, Tu hai meri..2

No birthday wishes - only release date questions for director Sriram Venu! Enjoy the entertaining video of release date announcement

Thammudu releasing worldwide on July 4th in theatres. The film stars Nithiin, Sapthami Gowda, Laya, Varsha Bollamma and others in key roles. Directed by Sriram Venu. Sri Venkateswara Creations bankrolling the film.


Cast: Nithiin, Sapthami Gowda, Laya, Varsha Bollamma, Saurabh Sachdeva, Swasika, Hari Teja, Srikanth Iyyengar, Temper Vamshi, Chammak Chandra And Others.
